{"tid":1067821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉事列車仍未拖走　荃灣綫金鐘至中環今早繼續停駛","createTime":"2019-03-18T20:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T23:12:59.000Z","uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"36636c2806e771f201cdec888dcde2a611a6bf96","tid":1067821,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:22:04.000Z","msg":"港鐵發言人於今日(19日)凌晨4時公佈：為配合中環站附近的復修工作，荃灣綫今早來往金鐘站和中環站服務暫停。來往荃灣站和金鐘站維持三分半鐘一班車。港鐵呼籲前往中環站乘客，可於金鐘站轉乘港島綫，乘客亦可考慮使用其他鐵路綫或其他公共交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/alert/alert_simpletxt_title_tc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Falert%2Falert_simpletxt_title_tc.html&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=35bcfb47\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/alert/alert_simpletxt_title_tc.html</a>"},{"pid":"2cc1a94b134ffdc0a61cf0ea513c16550197f71b","tid":1067821,"uid":220701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:26:18.000Z","msg":"不如搞到去星期五<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d459c10e06c2b62e1e6b7b96b353b33459307317","tid":1067821,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:30:41.000Z","msg":"撞到咁,隨時要就地解體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b703cc58c76e8ca8b45f19bc064ae4571fc681c","tid":1067821,"uid":16676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T21:18:06.000Z","msg":"呢兩晚早d 收車, 早d 通知咪得囉<br />\n有晒交通配合, 起碼多幾粒鐘做野"},{"pid":"f0a1e2a08c2f61b69a3f77e4186cb44f6a06691f","tid":1067821,"uid":16676,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T21:21:43.000Z","msg":"直接將果度做expo 展覽, <strong>炒車紀念博物館</strong>算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d621cc3c5105bd67fe6bc9b6ff1e850f8424b9","tid":1067821,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T21:21:48.000Z","msg":"夾硬拖 隨時拖爛埋條隧道"},{"pid":"853